This initiative delivers a programme of intensive research and innovation support to SMEs engaged in transport equipment manufacturing product and process technologies and associated supply chains.  The support will -
i) proactively identify opportunities for research and innovation collaboration between SMEs and  research institutes;
ii) provide finance to assist SMEs to access support provided by specialised research institutes across the UK and further afield;
iii) allow project partners to deliver research and innovation collaborations with target SMEs.

It will assist transport equipment manufacturing SMEs to promote their competitiveness by developing more efficient processes and products, boosting turnover and creating jobs

